quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,“۞ Ndithu apambana okhulupirira (mwa Allah)
  23,2,“Amene amakhudzumuka pa mapemphero awo (poipereka mitima yawo kwa Allah modzichepetsa)
  23,3,“Ndi omwe amapewa zinthu zopanda pake (zachabe)
  23,4,“Ndi omwe amakwaniritsa (nsanamira ya) chopereka (Zakaat)
  23,5,“Ndi omwe amasunga umaliseche wawo
  23,6,“Kupatula kwa akazi awo ndi adzakazi omwe manja awo akumanja apeza. Choncho iwo (pakukumana ndi amenewo) saali odzudzulidwa
  23,7,“Koma omwe angafune zosemphana ndi izi (kulumikizana ndi mkazi posiya njira ziwirizi) iwowo ndiwo opyola malire (a Allah)
  23,8,“Ndi amene amasunga malonjezo awo ndi zomwe akhulupirika nazo
  23,9,“Ndi omwe akusunga mapemphero awo (popemphera mu nthawi zake ndi kutsata malamulo ake uku ali odzichepetsa)
  23,10,“Iwo ndi olandira (zabwino tsiku la Qiyâma)
  23,11,“Amene adzalandira Munda wamtendere (wotchedwa) Fir’dausi (Munda wapamwamba kwambiri). M’menemo iwo adzakhala nthawi yaitali
  23,12,“Ndipo ndithu tidamlenga munthu kuchokera ku dongo labwino
  23,13,“Kenako tidalenga ana ake ndi dontho lamadzi (ambewu ya munthu) lomwe lidaikidwa pamalo osungidwa
  23,14,"“Kenako tidalisintha dontholo kukhala magazi oundana; ndipo kenako magaziwo tidawasintha kukhala m’nofu; ndipo kenako m’nofu tidausintha kukhala mafupa; ndipo mafupawo tidawaveka minofu, kenako tidamsintha kukhala cholengedwa china. Choncho watukuka Allah, Wabwino polenga"
  23,15,“Kenako ndithu inu pambuyo pa zimenezo mudzamwalira
  23,16,"“Ndithu inu, kenako mudzaukitsidwa pa tsiku la Qiyâma"
  23,17,"“Ndipo ndithu tapanga njira zisanu ndi ziwiri (mitambo) pamwamba panu, ndipo ndithu (Ife) sitisiya kulabadira zolengedwa"
  23,18,"“Ndipo tatsitsa madzi mwamuyeso kuchokera kumwamba, ndi kuwakhazikitsa m’nthaka; ndipo ndithu Ife ndi okhoza kuwachotsa (kuti musathandizike nawo, koma sitidachite zimenezo chifukwa chokuchitirani chifundo)"
  23,19,"“Ndi madzi amenewo, tidakupangirani minda ya kanjedza ndi mpesa, m’menemo inu mulinazo zipatso zambiri; ndipo mwazimenezo mumadya"
  23,20,"“Ndipo (tidakupangirani) mtengo womera pa phiri la Sinai, womwe umatulutsa mafuta; ndipo ndindiwo kwa amene amadya. (Mtengo wake ndi mzitona)"
  23,21,“Ndipo ndithu m’ziweto muli lingaliro kwa inu. Timakumwetsani zomwe zili m’mimba mwake; ndipo m’zimenezo mukupeza zothandiza zambiri; ndipo zina mwa izo mumadya
  23,22,"“Ndipo pa msana pa izo ndi pamwamba pa zombo, mumanyamulidwa"
  23,23,"“Ndipo ndithu tidamtuma Nuh kwa anthu ake, ndipo adati: “E inu anthu anga! Mpembedzeni Allah! Mulibe mulungu wina woti nkumpembedza kupatula Iye. Kodi simuopa (chilango Chake)"
  23,24,"“Akuluakulu mwa anthu ake amene sadakhulupirire, adati: “Uyu sali kanthu, koma ndi munthu ngati inu; akufuna kuti adzipezere ubwino pa inu; ndipo Allah akadafuna (kukuphunzitsani) akadatuma angelo. Zoterezi sitidamvepo kumakolo athu akale.”"
  23,25,"““Uyu sali kanthu, koma ndi munthu wamisala; choncho muyembekezereni mpaka nthawi (yofera.”)"
  23,26,"“(Nuh) adati: “Mbuye wanga ndipulumutseni pazomwe anditsutsa!”"
  23,27,"“Choncho tidamuvumbulutsira (mawu akuti): “Panga chombo moyang’aniridwa ndi kudziwitsidwa ndi Ife.” Ndipo lamulo Lathu likadza ndi kufwamphuka madzi mu uvuni, lowetsa mkati mwake (mwa chombocho) chilichonse ziwiriziwiri, chachimuna ndi chachikazi ndi banja lako, kupatula yemwe liwu latsogola pa iye kuti aonongeke mwa iwo. Ndipo usandilankhule za omwe adzichitira (okha) zoipa ndithu iwo amizidwa (m’madzi)"
  23,28,"“Ndipo ukakhazikika m’chombocho, iwe ndi amene uli nawo, nena: “Tikuthokoza Allah, amene watipulumutsa ku anthu osalungama.”"
  23,29,"“Ndipo (potsika), nena: “E Mbuye wanga! Nditsitseni; kutsitsa kwa madalitso, pakuti Inu ndinu wotsitsa bwino kwambiri kuposa otsitsa.”"
  23,30,“Ndithu m’zimenezi muli zisonyezo. Ndithu Ife tili (ndi udindo) wowayesa ndi mayeso osiyanasiyana
  23,31,“Kenako tidabweretsa m’badwo wina pambuyo pawo (omwe ndi Âdi)
  23,32,"“Ndipo tidatuma kwa iwo mtumiki (Hûd) wochokera mwa iwo, (yemwe ankati): “Pembedzani Allah! Mulibe mulungu wina kupatula Iye. Kodi simuopa"
  23,33,"“Ndipo akuluakulu a mwa anthu ake amene adali osakhulupirira, ndikutsutsa za kukumana ndi tsiku la chimaliziro, omwe tidawapatsa kulemera pa moyo wa padziko lapansi, adati: “Uyu saali kanthu, koma ndi munthu monga inu; amadya zimene inu mumadya, ndi kumwa zomwe inu mumamwa"
  23,34,"“Koma ngati mumvera munthu wonga inu, ndiye kuti mukhala otaika (oluza)"
  23,35,"“Kodi akukulonjezani kuti mukadzafa ndikusanduka dothi ndi mafupa, mudzaukitsidwanso (m’manda)"